These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
City: new-york, berlin, hamburg, colone
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, june, april
4 different games are played: domino, monopoly, mah-jongg, whist
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
10. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person traveling to new-york##7
11. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| City   | colone    | berlin | hamburg    | new-york   |
| Birthday   | january | june | march | april |
| Game           | monopoly       | mah-jongg   | whist  | domino     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

