.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, onion, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, train, quad-bike
House: futuristic, art-deco, farmhouse, townhouse
City: edinburgh, marseilles, berlin, hannover
 1. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 2. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
 3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the person traveling to berlin is the futuristic house##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 6. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the futuristic house##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
10. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
11. the art-deco house is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot   | onion       | watermelon    | mango      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | quad-bike | car         | train   |
| House   | townhouse   | futuristic  | art-deco       | farmhouse |
| City         | edinburgh      | berlin  | hannover | marseilles |

