.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, folk, house
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, orange, ivory, grey
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, domino, monopoly
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the person who likes ivory##7
 3. the fan of classical is the person playing go##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 5. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
 7. the fan of folk is not the person who likes orange##6
 8. the person who likes ivory is not the fan of house##6
 9. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
11. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
12. the person playing domino is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Music-Genre           | house | gospel | classical | folk |
| Color   | emerald        | grey    | orange    | ivory    |
| Game   | scrabble        | monopoly   | go   | domino         |
| Pet           | goat          | dog       | lizard   | horse           |

