 5. the person eating strawberry is not the person watching comedy movies##6
 6. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who likes emerald##6
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
