.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, march, november, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, thriller, fantasy, family
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, daisy, marigold
 1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 3. the person watching family movies is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsdaisy##2
 4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who growsaconite##6
 6. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's birthday is in june##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 9. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person who growsdaisy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | tea     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Birthday       | june   | august | march | november    |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy | family | comedy   | thriller  |
| Flower        | marigold | tulip     | daisy   | aconite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, soy-milk, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, blend, tiparillo
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, goldfish, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, taxi, ship
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the person driving the helicopter is between the blend-smoker and the owner of the fish##2
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the motorbike is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the tiparillo-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##7
 8. the person driving the helicopter is not the old-henry-smoker##6
 9. the owner of the bird is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
11. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the blend-smoker is not the person drinking fanta##6
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
14. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
15. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | 7up        | water          | soy-milk    |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | baccarat    | blend          | old-henry |
| Pet           | fish  | guinea-pig   | goldfish | bird      |
| Transport   | ship       | helicopter | taxi          | motorbike        |

