.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, potato, artichoke, grapes
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, soul, techno, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, quad-bike, car
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the fan of techno is the person eating artichoke##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person eating grapes and the person eating potato##2
 5. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
 6. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person eating raspberry##7
 7. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5
 8. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
10. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food   | grapes      | artichoke     | potato   | raspberry    |
| Music-Genre     | jazz | techno   | soul | electronic |
| Transport     | car        | quad-bike     | taxi  | bike      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 